Subject: drm/amdgpu: Add ring reset callback for JPEG4_0_3
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: c4c3808feb9c279a66519a064908cd06e5800da5
